data.description:
Welcome to 134 Pebble Ln in Cornerstone Subdivision, Harlem, Georgia. 1 owner, 4 beds, 2 full baths has 1961sqft home has tons of upgrades that is listed below. 

Home has crown molding through your main living areas, exposed beams, ship lap wall, accent wall in dining room, all fixtures upgraded, blinds on all windows, in-ceiling speakers in kitchen and living room, Duration paint through out entire home, quartz counter tops in kitchen and granite in all bathrooms, tile back splash in kitchen, outdoor kitchen that includes refrigerator and flat top griddle, outdoor speakers, screened in porch and outdoor deck, concrete curbing, gutters and privacy fenced in yard. 

Home is perfect for entertaining and has a split open floor plan, very spacious.

Cornerstone is close to I-20, Fort Gordon and is one exit away from shopping and restaurants.
